{"tid":861121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【攞命自拍】27樓露台憑欄自拍 女子意外墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-10-14T00:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T01:01:19.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a32f52498d63aa917d729d792d09f32cfb37979","tid":861121,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181014/58792302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58792302&d=MQUFF1JQbQWlVJcwYZXh9MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1349db59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58792302&h=3748ac88\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181014/58792302</a><br />\n在中美洲巴拿馬，一名女子在一幢大廈27樓的露台倚欄自拍時，意外墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n死者是27歲女子瑪沙度(Sandra Macedo)，她周五上午10時倚著露台欄河自拍時不慎墮下，過程被對面樓層目擊者拍下，影片可聽見拍片者大喊「她瘋了，看看她，看看她，噢，她掉下去了」。<br />\n<br />\n救護員接報到場，證實瑪沙度已當場死亡。當地報道指當局正調查事件，警方懷疑當時突刮起一陣風，令她失去平衡墮下。<br />\n<br />\n巴拿馬消防處事後在官方Twitter上發出警告訊息，表示「不要為自拍而冒生命危險...在一分鐘內失掉生命遠比人生中失掉一分鐘重要」。"},{"pid":"96c3a4511c59c53a24c5a1040a2c543d0a2c3d0e","tid":861121,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"27樓，27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c641a275b002d3f231dca68e02dc23e59653a47","tid":861121,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c3a4511c59c53a24c5a1040a2c543d0a2c3d0e","tid":861121,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"27樓，27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T01:01:19.000Z","msg":"loop到變化石啦，難為你仲覺得有趣"}]}